---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
import BuybackTracker from "@/components/token/BuybackTracker.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "Information about the $COWSAYS token, including tokenomics, buyback mechanism, and contract details.",
	title: "$COWSAYS Token",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<section>
		<h1 class="title mb-6">$COWSAYS Token</h1>
		<p class="mb-4">
			$COWSAYS is the official token of the Cowsay ecosystem. Built on Solana, this token represents the community
			around the daily developer quotes shared by the @cowsayco Twitter bot.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2 class="title mb-6 mt-16 text-2xl">Token Information</h2>
		
		<dl class="space-y-4">
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
				<dt>
					<span class="font-bold">Token Name</span>
				</dt>
				<dd>COWSAYS</dd>
			</div>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
				<dt>
					<span class="font-bold">Symbol</span>
				</dt>
				<dd>$COWSAYS</dd>
			</div>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
				<dt>
					<span class="font-bold">Blockchain</span>
				</dt>
				<dd>Solana</dd>
			</div>
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
				<dt>
					<span class="font-bold">Contract Address</span>
				</dt>
				<dd class="font-mono break-all">
					<span id="contract-address">[To be added after launch]</span>
				</dd>
			</div>
		</dl>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2 class="title mb-6 mt-16 text-2xl">Tokenomics</h2>
		
		<div class="mb-4">
			<p class="mb-2"><strong>Total Supply:</strong> 1,000,000,000 (1B fixed)</p>
			<p class="mb-4">
				The creator holds exactly <strong>20% of the total supply</strong> (200M tokens) with a 10-year vesting lock using Streamflow (popular & trusted). The remaining 80% is available for public trading via fair bonding curve + DEX.
			</p>
		</div>

		<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-4">
			<li><strong>Creator Allocation:</strong> 20% (200M tokens) - 10-year vesting lock via Streamflow</li>
			<li><strong>Public Distribution:</strong> 80% (800M tokens) - via fair bonding curve + DEX</li>
			<li><strong>No Burning:</strong> All tokens are held</li>
			<li><strong>On-chain Verification:</strong> Vesting lock is verifiable on-chain from day 1</li>
			<li><strong>Public Commitment:</strong> Creator vows NO SALES for 10 years from launch</li>
		</ul>

		<p class="mb-4">
			For detailed tokenomics information, see the <a class="cactus-link" href="https://github.com/meowso/cowsay/blob/main/TOKENOMICS.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">TOKENOMICS.md</a> file in the repository.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2 class="title mb-6 mt-16 text-2xl">Buyback Mechanism</h2>
		
		<p class="mb-4">
			All profits from the Cowsay ecosystem are automatically reinvested into $COWSAYS token buybacks:
		</p>

		<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-4">
			<li><strong>Merchandise Shop:</strong> All profits from T-shirts, mugs, mousepads, and other products</li>
			<li><strong>NFT Auctions:</strong> All proceeds from auctioned quote artwork NFTs</li>
			<li><strong>Future Revenue:</strong> Any additional revenue generated by the Cowsay ecosystem</li>
		</ul>

		<p class="mb-4">
			This creates a sustainable buyback mechanism where the success of the Cowsay brand directly benefits token
			holders through continuous buybacks for 10 years.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2 class="title mb-6 mt-16 text-2xl">Buyback History</h2>
		
		<BuybackTracker />
	</section>

	<section>
		<h2 class="title mb-6 mt-16 text-2xl">Links</h2>
		
		<ul class="space-y-2">
			<li>
				<a class="cactus-link" href="https://dexscreener.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
					Dexscreener Chart
				</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a class="cactus-link" href="/transparency">Transparency Dashboard</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a class="cactus-link" href="https://github.com/meowso/cowsay/blob/main/TOKENOMICS.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Full Tokenomics</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				<a class="cactus-link" href="https://github.com/meowso/cowsay/blob/main/TRANSPARENCY.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Transparency & Commitment</a>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>
</PageLayout>

